title: FXhome Imerge Pro 1.2.0 Full + Medicine[BabuPC]
description:
FXhome Imerge Pro
Create pro-level composites with unlimited layers and zero baked-in changes. Imerge Pro is the first photo editing software to keep your image data RAW and your layers self-contained. Every edit is live. Every change is flexible. No need to hide and show layers to compare different compositions – each layer can hold multiple images or text items for every variation.

Composite faster with 38 filters
Want more vibrant colors or crisp, clear edge detail in seconds? Scale up image quality and cut down editing time with Imerge Pro filter effects.

– Black & white
– Bleach bypass
– Channel viewer
– Chroma key
– Clarity
– Clouds
– Color adjustment
– Color difference key
– Color overlay
– Curves
– Dehaze
– Directional blur
– Exposure
– Gaussian blur
– Grain
– Inner glow
– Invert
– LUT (look-up table)
– Levels
– Light wrap
– Linear gradient
– Luminance key
